        </div>
        
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          Property-Backed Lending
          <span class="gradient-text">Made Simple</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="hero-description">
          Streamline real estate financing from application to closing. Our platform handles residential, commercial, and mixed-use properties with intelligent valuation and risk assessment.
        </p>
        
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="https://calendly.com/contact-mentyx/30min" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary animated-btn">
            Schedule a Demo
