          <div class="stat-label">Borrower Satisfaction</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-value">60%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Faster Processing</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Enhanced Features Section -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Powerful Features</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Comprehensive Real Estate Lending</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          End-to-end platform for all property types and financing structures
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
              <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Automated Valuation</h3>
          <p>AI-powered property valuations using comps, market data, and property characteristics. Get instant estimates with 95% accuracy.</p>
          <div class="feature-highlight">95% Accuracy</div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Fast Underwriting</h3>
          <p>Reduce underwriting time from weeks to days. Automated document collection, verification, and risk assessment workflows.</p>
          <div class="feature-highlight">Weeks â†’ Days</div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/>
              <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Multi-Property Support</h3>
          <p>Handle residential, commercial, industrial, and mixed-use properties. Support for single-family, multi-family, and portfolios.</p>
          <div class="feature-highlight">All Property Types</div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M20 7h-9"/>
              <path d="M14 17H5"/>
              <circle cx="17" cy="17" r="3"/>
              <circle cx="7" cy="7" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Flexible Structures</h3>
          <p>Support for purchase, refinance, construction, bridge, and permanent financing. Customize terms and structure for any deal.</p>
          <div class="feature-highlight">Customizable</div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2v20m5-17H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Title & Insurance</h3>
          <p>Integrated title search, insurance ordering, and closing coordination. Streamline the entire closing process.</p>
          <div class="feature-highlight">Fully Integrated</div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Market Analytics</h3>
          <p>Real-time market data, trend analysis, and risk indicators. Make informed lending decisions with comprehensive insights.</p>
          <div class="feature-highlight">Real-time Data</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Streamlined Process</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">From Application to Closing in Record Time</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          Our automated workflow reduces traditional processing time by 60% while improving accuracy
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Application & Documentation</h3>
            <p>Borrower submits application through our intuitive portal with automated document collection and verification.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Automated Valuation</h3>
            <p>AI-powered property assessment using market comps, satellite imagery, and property data for instant valuation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Risk Assessment</h3>
            <p>Machine learning models analyze borrower credit, property risk, and market conditions for comprehensive underwriting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">04</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Approval & Closing</h3>
            <p>Automated approval workflows with integrated title, insurance, and closing coordination for seamless execution.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Enhanced Benefits Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Why Choose mentyx</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Transform Your Real Estate Lending Operations</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-item">
          <div class="benefit-number">01</div>
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0 1 12 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 0 1-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 3 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Property Intelligence</h3>
          <p>Advanced property analysis using AI to assess value, condition, and market position with unmatched accuracy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-item">
          <div class="benefit-number">02</div>
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 0 0-8 0v4h8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Regulatory Compliance</h3>
          <p>Built-in compliance checks for TILA, RESPA, and state lending regulations. Automatic documentation and audit trails.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-item">
          <div class="benefit-number">03</div>
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M8 17h8m-8-4h8m4 4v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6l2 2h6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Third-Party Integration</h3>
          <p>Connect with appraisers, title companies, inspectors, and closing agents through our integrated network.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-item">
          <div class="benefit-number">04</div>
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 0 0-9-9m9 9H3m9 9v-9m0-9a9 9 0 0 0-9 9"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Borrower Portal</h3>
          <p>White-labeled portal for borrowers to submit documents, track progress, and communicate throughout the loan process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Enhanced CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <div class="cta-badge">Get Started Today</div>
        <h2>Transform Your Real Estate Lending</h2>
        <p>See how mentyx can help you close more deals faster with better borrower experiences.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="https://calendly.com/contact-mentyx/30min" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            Schedule a Demo
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M5 12h14m-7-7l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="javascript:window.openModal()" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
            Contact Sales
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Enhanced Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    padding: 160px 0 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--slate-900) 0%, var(--slate-800) 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-background {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .floating-shapes {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .shape {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.05) 100%);
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .shape-1 {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    top: 20%;
    left: 10%;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .shape-2 {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    top: 60%;
    right: 10%;
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }

  .shape-3 {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    bottom: 20%;
    left: 20%;
    animation-delay: 4s;
  }

  .shape-4 {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    top: 30%;
    right: 20%;
    animation-delay: 1s;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(10deg); }
  }

  .hero-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    color: var(--cyan-400);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .animated-badge {
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-500) 0%, var(--cyan-500) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--slate-300);
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }

  .animated-btn:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .btn-primary svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  /* Enhanced Stats Grid */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .stat-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1), transparent);
    transition: left 0.5s;
  }

  .stat-card:hover::before {
    left: 100%;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .stat-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--cyan-400);
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .stat-card:hover .stat-icon {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-500) 0%, var(--cyan-500) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: var(--slate-400);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Enhanced Features Section */
  .features-section,
  .benefits-section,
  .process-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--slate-900);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    color: var(--cyan-400);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--slate-400);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8) 0%, rgba(10, 16, 28, 0.9) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue-500), var(--cyan-500));
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover::before {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--cyan-400);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--slate-400);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .feature-highlight {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--cyan-400);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Process Section */
  .process-steps {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .process-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6) 0%, rgba(10, 16, 28, 0.8) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .process-step:hover {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    transform: translateX(8px);
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-500) 0%, var(--cyan-500) 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--slate-400);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Enhanced Benefits Section */
  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 40px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .benefit-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 24px;
